    "For instance, polymers can exhibit heterogeneous compositions within a single chain (e.g. copolymers).",
    "With multiple polymer chains, they can mix, blend and entangle to form high-level intricate polymer networks.",
    "These compositional and structural variations play a crucial role in determining the electrochemical properties of polymers.",
    "Moreover, inside a battery, there are salts and other additives that actively interact with polymer electrolytes.",
    "The combination of these materials strongly affects the overall performance of the battery."
